{"tid":866073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵通車】直達上海虹橋班次下月11日起暫停 職員：未知何時恢復","createTime":"2018-10-17T14:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T05:21:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"56c122cee150104c3102f1a0c9ae7a602986d72b","tid":866073,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181017/large/1539779479_a0d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181017%2Flarge%2F1539779479_a0d8.jpg&h=a9677039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段自上月23日通車，每日都有往來香港西九龍至上海虹橋的班次。今日傍晚突傳出消息，指11月11日起往來上海虹橋的車次G99及G100的車票預售服務暫停，意味唯一一對往來上海虹橋的直達列車，暫時無法提供服務。《蘋果》致電客務熱綫查詢，職員表示暫未知相關班次何時恢復。 <br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》以顧客身份致電客務熱綫查詢，職員稱由11月11日當日起，西九往上海虹橋的高鐵班次將會暫停，可能是由於車務調動，暫時不知何時恢復。職員表示，旅客如必須乘搭高鐵出發到上海虹橋，可先乘搭到內地再轉車。至於轉車詳情，職員就指不太清楚，着顧客到西九站內的中國鐵路櫃位查詢內地段購票詳情。<br />\n<br />\n職員又表示，預售記錄只能看到1個月內的資料，故目前只知道11月11日至15日，都沒有西九至上海虹橋的班次，其後的日子就要稍後再查詢。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵網頁於下午5時多發出告示，指「收到中國鐵路廣州局通知，受鐵路施工工程影響，由2018年11月11日起，往來香港西九龍及上海虹橋的車次G99及G100 的行車時間表或會有所調整，於上述時間開出的該列車的車票預售服務將暫停，直至另行通知。」乘客可致電客務熱綫21200888查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181017/large/1539780600_c336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181017%2Flarge%2F1539780600_c336.jpg&h=48a260c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳港鐵站內貼出告示，同樣指11月11日起往來西九及上海虹橋的車次暫停預售車票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181017/58805642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58805642&d=nBraoQCGKGaI3WirSl3E3bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7ceaf062\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58805642&h=fd027c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181017/58805642</a>"},{"pid":"034e628c4858da754adc5e606bff50cd531c82d9","tid":866073,"uid":95497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"等睇cut到0班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c99cae9c19060a1193fc7bbaf04fc1d469c40e0","tid":866073,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"咁快就cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a02a6761204e1566b55c94ce590e5ef430f135","tid":866073,"uid":20658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"咁快收皮啦"},{"pid":"21a6f1d8dd8cb51fa72b14766d148223ea122246","tid":866073,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"別國內政"},{"pid":"126e83baf8fea107665b411d8cb606bfd48e79a5","tid":866073,"uid":38109,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"可先乘搭到內地再轉車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5ce1e444c0fc65d5efb1a2f75c881d5c6f11e9","tid":866073,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"cut上海做乜"},{"pid":"145c309d67797a6dd0a601d0cf4a08e05fdba1d8","tid":866073,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"原來大陸有野維修"},{"pid":"d69f7b5f10e22f01f6ceb8aa6ffd992ae38bdac0","tid":866073,"uid":21917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"係咪計下計下發現 唔係長假既日子連本都回唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29d4f007066e56ebdee38aff5eda8f6a331505d","tid":866073,"uid":4781,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"cut到變紅van咁坐滿先開車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5d9ff5718eca8da3070db2af0